"Hi! I'm Amanda Lynn, and I'm passionate about creating beautiful, authentic content that tells your culinary story. Whether you're a restaurant looking to showcase your latest menu, a food brand wanting to highlight your products, or a destination seeking to share your unique flavors with the world, I'd love to help bring your vision to life.\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"text-foreground/70 leading-relaxed\",\"children\":\"With years of experience in food photography, recipe development, and culinary storytelling, I specialize in creating engaging content across Instagram Reels, Instagram Stories, and blog posts. My goal is to help you connect with food lovers and grow your audience through compelling visuals and genuine narratives.\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"text-foreground/70 leading-relaxed\",\"children\":\"Let's collaborate to highlight what makes your restaurant, brand, or destination special and create content that resonates with your audience!\"}]]}]]}]}],[\"$\",\"section\",null,{\"className\":\"max-w-[1200px] mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 md:px-8 lg:px-12 xl:px-16 mb-16 sm:mb-24\",\"children\":[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"space-y-10 sm:space-y-16 lg:space-y-24\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"flex flex-col lg:flex-row-reverse gap-8 lg:gap-12 items-center\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"lg:w-1/2\",\"children\":[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"polaroid-image-right mx-auto\",\"children\":[\"$\",\"$L5\",null,{\"src\":\"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1564758596018-3e5b1f2340cc?crop=entropy&cs=tinysrgb&fit=max&fm=jpg&ixid=M3w3Nzg4Nzd8MHwxfHNlYXJjaHwxfHxwaG9uZSUyMGluc3RhZ3JhbSUyMGZvb2R8ZW58MXx8fHwxNzYyNzI4MjI3fDA&ixlib=rb-4.1.0&q=80&w=1080\",\"alt\":\"Instagram Reels on phone\",\"width\":400,\"height\":500,\"className\":\"w-full h-auto\"}]}]}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"lg:w-1/2 space-y-4\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"flex items-center gap-3 mb-4\",\"children\":[[\